data.name: rtbGuide.Text
data.value:
1. Users must have an account to play CaroGame. So if you haven't had an account, please click button "Register" to create one. If you had accounts, let click button "Login" to enter the game.
2. Game Rules: The player can create a set of 5 consecutive chess pieces horizontally, vertically or diagonally first will win this game.
3. There are two play modes for users: "play with computer" or "play with player". - On PlayWithComputer mode, Computer will play chess first. Once the match is over, it will continue to the next match. If you are playing with Computer and you are bored, then you can click New Game to begin a new match! If you play chess wrong, you can click Undo to play chess again! If you don't want to play CaroGame anymore, you can click Exit to get out of the game! - On PlayWithPlayer mode, before playing, 2 players need to set up connection by entering IP and Port. The player creating the server first - his chess color will be red. The other - his chess color will be purple!
4. Finally, good luck!
